### HTTP Status Codes
- **200**: Success
- **400**: Bad Request (validation errors)
- **401**: Unauthorized
- **403**: Forbidden (insufficient permissions)
- **404**: Not Found
- **422**: Unprocessable Entity (business logic errors)
- **500**: Internal Server Error

